{"tid":838353,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"法唔法國好多人冇錢買車養車又走去考車牌？","createTime":"2018-09-27T04:58:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T05:47:52.000Z","uid":131878,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0dd2828e0024299944c0edf881d38a2bc52e502e","tid":838353,"uid":131878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T04:58:56.000Z","msg":"自從上咗U之後身邊越黎越多人走去考車牌，<br />\n有啲朋友asso/hd grad搵得12 13k冇家底又去考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n考完日日袋住張駕駛執照但其實冇車揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上星期同朋友出街食飯<br />\n我=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  朋友=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n朋友開個銀包拎張駕駛執照俾我睇<br />\n<br />\n朋友: 喂睇下我張野到手喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我: 咦你咁快買咗車嗱？<br />\n<br />\n朋友: 痴線邊有錢買，諗住借其他人啲車黎揸咋。你屋企係咪有車，唔洗揸嗰時可唔可以借黎<br />\n<br />\n我:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(到底呢啲人係咪痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n咁你唔買車考黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n朋友: 考車係有錢人嘅象徵<br />\n<br />\n你贏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a04f7358253e296bc4837363add441b878e09a1","tid":838353,"uid":22115,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T05:00:52.000Z","msg":"牌都唔俾人考<img src=\"/assets/fa